## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="009f4-208">O exemplo a seguir define essa propriedade para usar ao enviar solicitações ao proxy especificado no <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.ProxyAddress%2A> propriedade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="009f4-208">The following example sets this property to use when sending requests to the proxy specified in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.ProxyAddress%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
HttpTransportBindingElement httpBinding = new HttpTransportBindingElement();  
httpBinding.ProxyAddress = new Uri(http://proxyserver);  
httpBinding.ProxyAuthenticationScheme = AuthenticationSchemes.Digest;  
```

  
  
